name: Parity The Game
blurb: Overrun by mutants, San Diego is in chaos on every street. Can you survive the first night in this moment in time?

name: Central San Diego
displayable_name: Central San Diego, San Diego, CA

rewards.reward: Our appreciation and thanks for your support. Like all backers you get your name in credits. Also, if we see you in public you get a hi-five, which is priceless!
You will get a personal thank you tweet from the Parity Team as well as being listed as a supporter on the credits of Parity. Don\u2019t worry, you also get the hi-five mentioned in tier 1.
Tiers 1-2  plus a digital download of the playable demo once complete.
Tiers 1-3 plus a personalized card/letter to include a picture of a pussy (as in the actual \u201cpussy cat\u201d animal) thanking you for your support.

Tiers 1-4, a digital download of the finished Parity game (Est. completion Summer 2015) upon completion, and a Parity t-shirt! Wear it to work, the park, on a hot date, or dress a pillow with it and cuddle up with it at night. We aren't here to judge!

Tiers 1-4 and a digital download of the finished Parity game (Est. completion Summer 2015) as well as being able to collaborate with the creator to either have your name featured on a billboard, advertisement, poster, or other item during game play. Even if your name is Norma Stitz or Harry Shlong we will make sure you are represented.

Tiers 1-4, digital download of the finished Parity game (Est. completion Summer 2015), plus you will also be given access to downloadable content not available to the public such as additional character abilities, weapons, and game play items. You get the ultimate VIP access without the dirty backstage dressing room!

Tiers 1-4, digital and physical creator signed copy of the finished Parity game upon completion (Est. Summer 2015). You will also be listed as a contributor on Parity credits and if you have a small business, band, project, or something else that you would like to promote (assuming it is legal, non-violent, and not in poor taste) we will agree to feature you not only on a tweet but on our Catatonic Overlord Studios website to be seen by all those who visit our webpage. If you don\u2019t have something you want to promote we will give you a personal shout out via video to be featured on the website and twitter (to be posted by October 2014)! We\u2019ll tell everyone how awesome you are!

Tiers 1-4, digital and physical signed copy of the finished Parity game upon completion (Est. Summer 2015), plus you will also be able to work with the creator of Parity to name a landmark after yourself such as a park, restaurant, school, or other location which the characters will visit and have interactions at so your name will be noticed by all who play Parity. Your name may not be famous in real life but can be in Parity!

Tiers 1-4, digital and signed copy of the finished Parity game upon completion (Est. 2015), as well as the opportunity to collaborate on the creation of a weapon to be featured in Parity which you will be listed as a contributor to on the Parity credits. You will work with the Parity team to design a unique and one of a kind item. You will get a framed illustration of this item sent to you prior to the release of the Parity game. Hang it in your bedroom, living room, bathroom, 2nd solarium or wherever your good ideas are displayed!

Tiers 1-4, digital and signed copy of the finished Parity game upon completion (Est. 2015), plus collaborate with the creator to design a character based on your likeness which will be featured in Parity with a speaking role to interact with the playable characters.You will get a framed illustration of this character sent to you prior to the release of Parity. You will be featured as a contributor in the credits and receive special recognition (thank you post) on the Catatonic Overlord Studios sites upon release of the Parity game to the public.
